  "title": "Understanding Timing and Rhythm",
  "lessonText": "Mastering timing and rhythm is essential for playing melodies accurately.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Timing refers to when you play notes.\n- Rhythm is the pattern of sounds and silences.\n- Use a metronome to practice steady beats.\n- Start with simple rhythms before progressing.\n- Count out loud to internalize timing.\n- Listen to music to understand rhythmic patterns."
  }
}
